Hi all,

I've received a couple of emails recently asking for assistance with 
SharpNEAT based experiments that I was unaware of, so I was thinking 
that maybe it's time for another roll call of NEAT projects and research 
that people on the list are working on and/or know about.

As for SharpNEAT, there's not much actual work going on right now 
although I'm hoping to put together a SharpNEAT roadmap for 2005 some 
time soon. However, the way things are going this will probably become 
the 2006 roadmap :)

Colin
